{"tid":2149872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麥當勞起訴前CEO 曾與多名雇員發生性關係 要求討回遣散費","createTime":"2020-08-10T15:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T15:50:48.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a83f7e961db0531f0cc714e94b5805e0ab3436","tid":2149872,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T15:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X7QU4sIBL_I8AUO1kOYz4w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f8798d5927239c56ac01e3cfb739447e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FX7QU4sIBL_I8AUO1kOYz4w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbloomberg_chinese_traditional_757%2Ff8798d5927239c56ac01e3cfb739447e&h=5643235f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【彭博】-- 麥當勞發現證據顯示，被罷免的原執行長Steve Easterbrook曾與多名雇員發生性關係，試圖予以掩蓋，並安排一名員工獲得豐厚的股票獎勵，由此決定對他提起訴訟，以討回數千萬美元的遣散費。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞在公告中稱，去年秋季，Easterbrook因與一名員工存在自願性關係而被解職時，不應獲取遣散費，因為他「掩蓋證據，並對自己的不當行為說謊」。麥當勞表示，上月收到匿名舉報後，在Easterbrook的公司電郵賬號中發現露骨的照片，還發現了顯示他與其他雇員發生不當關係的證據。<br />\n<br />\n因此，快餐連鎖巨頭麥當勞向特拉華州的一家法院提起訴訟，要求討回Easterbrook離職後取得的一切補償和遣散費。公司還採取行動，阻止Easterbrook對股票期權行權或出售股票。"},{"pid":"6eae6b5d74bcfd554a7b1572c931a0f84aa15dd0","tid":2149872,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"秒撚準備"},{"pid":"e92e38684d5384c6369d5dfecd94032518aad54a","tid":2149872,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"Im fuckin it"}]}